snippet.title: Age of Empires: The Rise of Rome
snippet.description: The Rise of Rome is an expansion to the real-time strategy game  Age of Empires. It has been developed by Ensemble Studios and published by Microsoft in 1998. Based on the rise of the Roman Empire, it adds the Roman Empire and three other civilizations to the original game.
